        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;');
            return json.replace(/("(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\"])*"(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d+(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][+\-]?\d+)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = 'number';
                if (/^"/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = 'key';
                    } else {
                        cls = 'string';
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'boolean';
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'null';
                }
                return '<span class="' + cls + '">' + match + '</span>';
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);

        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;');
            return json.replace(/("(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\"])*"(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d+(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][+\-]?\d+)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = 'number';
                if (/^"/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = 'key';
                    } else {
                        cls = 'string';
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'boolean';
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'null';
                }
                return '<span class="' + cls + '">' + match + '</span>';
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }
    </script>

        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;');
            return json.replace(/("(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\"])*"(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d+(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][+\-]?\d+)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = 'number';
                if (/^"/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = 'key';
                    } else {
                        cls = 'string';
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'boolean';
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'null';
                }
                return '<span class="' + cls + '">' + match + '</span>';
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }

        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&amp;amp;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;amp;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;lt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;lt;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;gt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;gt;&amp;#39;);
            return json.replace(/(&amp;#34;(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\&amp;#34;])*&amp;#34;(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d&amp;#43;(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][&amp;#43;\-]?\d&amp;#43;)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = &amp;#39;number&amp;#39;;
                if (/^&amp;#34;/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = &amp;#39;key&amp;#39;;
                    } else {
                        cls = &amp;#39;string&amp;#39;;
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;boolean&amp;#39;;
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;null&amp;#39;;
                }
                return &amp;#39;&amp;lt;span class=&amp;#34;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; cls &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; match &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;#39;;
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }

    <script>
         
        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&/g, '&amp;').replace(/</g, '&lt;').replace(/>/g, '&gt;');
            return json.replace(/("(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\"])*"(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d+(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][+\-]?\d+)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = 'number';
                if (/^"/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = 'key';
                    } else {
                        cls = 'string';
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'boolean';
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = 'null';
                }
                return '<span class="' + cls + '">' + match + '</span>';
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }
    </script>

        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&amp;amp;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;amp;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;lt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;lt;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;gt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;gt;&amp;#39;);
            return json.replace(/(&amp;#34;(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\&amp;#34;])*&amp;#34;(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d&amp;#43;(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][&amp;#43;\-]?\d&amp;#43;)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = &amp;#39;number&amp;#39;;
                if (/^&amp;#34;/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = &amp;#39;key&amp;#39;;
                    } else {
                        cls = &amp;#39;string&amp;#39;;
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;boolean&amp;#39;;
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;null&amp;#39;;
                }
                return &amp;#39;&amp;lt;span class=&amp;#34;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; cls &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; match &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;#39;;
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }

        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&amp;amp;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;amp;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;lt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;lt;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;gt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;gt;&amp;#39;);
            return json.replace(/(&amp;#34;(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\&amp;#34;])*&amp;#34;(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d&amp;#43;(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][&amp;#43;\-]?\d&amp;#43;)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = &amp;#39;number&amp;#39;;
                if (/^&amp;#34;/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = &amp;#39;key&amp;#39;;
                    } else {
                        cls = &amp;#39;string&amp;#39;;
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;boolean&amp;#39;;
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;null&amp;#39;;
                }
                return &amp;#39;&amp;lt;span class=&amp;#34;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; cls &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; match &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;#39;;
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }

    &amp;lt;script&amp;gt;
         
        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&amp;amp;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;amp;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;lt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;lt;&amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;gt;/g, &amp;#39;&amp;amp;gt;&amp;#39;);
            return json.replace(/(&amp;#34;(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\&amp;#34;])*&amp;#34;(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d&amp;#43;(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][&amp;#43;\-]?\d&amp;#43;)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = &amp;#39;number&amp;#39;;
                if (/^&amp;#34;/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = &amp;#39;key&amp;#39;;
                    } else {
                        cls = &amp;#39;string&amp;#39;;
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;boolean&amp;#39;;
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;#39;null&amp;#39;;
                }
                return &amp;#39;&amp;lt;span class=&amp;#34;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; cls &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;#34;&amp;gt;&amp;#39; &amp;#43; match &amp;#43; &amp;#39;&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;&amp;#39;;
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }
    &amp;lt;/script&amp;gt;

        function syntaxHighlight(json) {
            json = json.replace(/&amp;amp;amp;/g, &amp;amp;#39;&amp;amp;amp;amp;&amp;amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;amp;lt;/g, &amp;amp;#39;&amp;amp;amp;lt;&amp;amp;#39;).replace(/&amp;amp;gt;/g, &amp;amp;#39;&amp;amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;#39;);
            return json.replace(/(&amp;amp;#34;(\\u[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}|\\[^u]|[^\\&amp;amp;#34;])*&amp;amp;#34;(\s*:)?|\b(true|false|null)\b|-?\d&amp;amp;#43;(?:\.\d*)?(?:[eE][&amp;amp;#43;\-]?\d&amp;amp;#43;)?)/g, function (match) {
                var cls = &amp;amp;#39;number&amp;amp;#39;;
                if (/^&amp;amp;#34;/.test(match)) {
                    if (/:$/.test(match)) {
                        cls = &amp;amp;#39;key&amp;amp;#39;;
                    } else {
                        cls = &amp;amp;#39;string&amp;amp;#39;;
                    }
                } else if (/true|false/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;amp;#39;boolean&amp;amp;#39;;
                } else if (/null/.test(match)) {
                    cls = &amp;amp;#39;null&amp;amp;#39;;
                }
                return &amp;amp;#39;&amp;amp;lt;span class=&amp;amp;#34;&amp;amp;#39; &amp;amp;#43; cls &amp;amp;#43; &amp;amp;#39;&amp;amp;#34;&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;#39; &amp;amp;#43; match &amp;amp;#43; &amp;amp;#39;&amp;amp;lt;/span&amp;amp;gt;&amp;amp;#39;;
            });
        }

        function spaceJson(json){
            var validJson = JSON.parse(json);
            return JSON.stringify(validJson, undefined, 4);
        }
